{"tid":1589104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵請人！ 要求兩年警察或輔警之工作經驗！","createTime":"2019-09-23T06:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T06:32:59.000Z","uid":154004,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"871ec87c80796c22aac437ca550fc868315e2f9b","tid":1589104,"uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"經過黨鐵站成班呀叔呀嬸圍爐吹水，原來係「附例特檢隊」，上網check咩料，發現近排請人，專捉跳閘寶寶：<br />\n<br />\nMTR Corporation Limited 香 港 鐵 路 有 限 公 司<br />\n附 例 特 檢 隊 隊 目 (編 號 : 190000ZI)<br />\n<br />\nMTR Corporation Limited<br />\n香 港 鐵 路 有 限 公 司<br />\n<br />\n職務<br />\n<br />\n帶領隊員巡邏 、執行《香港鐵路附例》及查票工作<br />\n按照程序協助車站職員<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">檢控逃票行為並徵收有關罰款</span></span></strong>，及應付其他違例者的不恰當行為<br />\n防止乘客攜帶不符合公司現行規定的大型行李或危險物品進入鐵路範圍<br />\n控制車站人流及維持車站秩序<br />\n<br />\n資格<br />\n<br />\n香港中學會考/香港中學文憑程度<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩年警察或輔警之工作經驗</span></span></strong><br />\n曾出任執行《香港鐵路附例》相關工作之申請者可獲優先考慮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EBjLKqo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEBjLKqo.png&h=a696972d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家經過見到記得要關心吓啲變種狗！"},{"pid":"09bd0743e7b4d50f788375d9574ae1036c31edfd","tid":1589104,"uid":325882,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5426e3e238ee25c870961c23449cbcb4b5c3d82b","tid":1589104,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"bc15aaff697003cf2ffa61f679d00496a309e1ac","tid":1589104,"uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09bd